data.title: This Boy's in love
data.text:
kcwm

I prefer Beams a lot more than Apocolypto or whatever its called its just more of a hard hitting groove session rather than this new poppy dance direction they are going in....perhaps Daniel Johns is having too much of an influence on them in that regard But Daniel is awesome, I've heard rumors and semi confirmation that he helped do the vocals on the chorus of this song

Receiving transmission from David Bowie's nipple antenna. Do you read me Lieutenant Bowie, I said do you read me...Lieutenant Bowie

kcwm

They go off live tho! I've seen them like 5 or so times
